## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Language | Ruby {{RUBY_VERSION}} / Rails 8.x |
| Frontend | Hotwire (Turbo + Stimulus) + importmap-rails |
| CSS | Native CSS with cascade layers |
| Auth | Passwordless magic links |
| Jobs | Solid Queue |
| Cache | Solid Cache |
| WebSockets | Solid Cable |
| Deploy | Kamal |

## Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `bin/dev` | Start development server |
| `bin/rails test` | Run tests |
| `bin/ci` | Full CI suite (lint + tests) |
| `make lint` | Run rubocop |
| `make lint-fix` | Auto-fix lint offenses |
| `make deploy` | Deploy to production |
| `bin/rails routes` | List all routes |
| `bin/rails console` | Open Rails console |

